        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1317942053" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15060745216535243406"><strong>Great Book</strong><br/><br/>This is an excellent book. Once I started reading it I could not put it down until I finished it. I thoroughly enjoyed the characters and their relationship with each other. There is a lot of magical action. My favorite characters are Jason, Benjamin, Amy and Michelle. Monte surprised me. His true self was totally unexpected. I look forward to reading the next book in the series. I highly recommend this book. This book us a great read </span>

          </span>
        </div>


